  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 99-1-5, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT A PERSON SHALL NOT BE PROSECUTED FOR FELONIOUS ASSISTANCE PROGRAM FRAUD, AS DESCRIBED IN SECTION 97-19-71, UNLESS THE PROSECUTION FOR THE OFFENSE IS COMMENCED WITHIN TEN (10) YEARS AFTER THE COMMISSION THEREOF; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
